            <description><![CDATA[【多种油调换着吃！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%AA%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%B2%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%AA%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%B2%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#避免长期只吃一种油#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%AA%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%B2%B9%E6%88%96%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%AA%E5%90%83%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%B2%B9%E6%88%96%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长期只吃一种油或导致营养缺失#</span></a> 不同的不饱和脂肪酸对人体的健康有着不同的作用，长期单一地选择某一种类的食用油，有可能会导致人体的某些营养元素的不足。 <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WTuQxw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
