        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#不吃油脂或增加胆结石风险#】肥胖人群由于过量摄入高脂食物，容易导致胆汁里胆固醇含量增高，析出结晶，形成胆囊结石。同时，肥胖人群的糖类代谢和脂肪...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E6%B2%B9%E8%84%82%E6%88%96%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%86%E7%BB%93%E7%9F%B3%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%83%E6%B2%B9%E8%84%82%E6%88%96%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%86%E7%BB%93%E7%9F%B3%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不吃油脂或增加胆结石风险#</span></a>】肥胖人群由于过量摄入高脂食物，容易导致胆汁里胆固醇含量增高，析出结晶，形成胆囊结石。同时，肥胖人群的糖类代谢和脂肪代谢相对紊乱，也容易产生胆囊结石。但是，如果不进食油脂，胆囊里的胆汁会长时间储存并不断浓缩，反而增加患胆囊结石的风险。所以请记住，合理膳食！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6j8LesM" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
